Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7490060866866793e-47, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"only the second man\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"the same swimming event\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"three successive Olympics\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A competitive and thrilling final all came down to the final stroke, with Italy's Nicolo Martinenghi finishing just 0.02 seconds ahead of joint-silver medallists Peaty and American Nic Fink to clinch a shock gold.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.998680225178391, \"rank\": 0.0012290001957312485, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"score\": 0.9999999871765796, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolo Martinenghi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicol\\u00f2_Martinenghi\"}, {\"begin\": 627, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999437310190853, \"rank\": 4.682589188689524e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nic Fink\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nic_Fink\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final stroke\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"a shock gold\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Peaty was unable to make more history in the pool and take home a third gold medal, he did secure a sixth Olympic medal after returning to the sport following a break due to mental health issues and alcoholism.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"more history\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"a third gold medal\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"a sixth Olympic medal\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health issues\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"alcoholism\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty initially appeared in good spirits in an interview withBBC Sportstraight after the final but began to choke up as he reflected on his emotional and inspiring journey.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"good spirits\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"Sportstraight\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"his emotional and inspiring journey\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheParis 2024 silver medallistsaid: 'It has been a very long way back.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I look at the score there and you would never think in your wildest dreams that it would be 59 seconds to win it.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"your wildest dreams\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"59 seconds\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my heart I have already won\\\" \\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fAdam Peaty let all his emotions out after he won silver in the men's breaststroke final \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00a5We are very proud of you Adam!#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/JxUFvunn2Z 'I gave it my absolute all.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"all his emotions\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's breaststroke final \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u00a5We\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"you Adam!#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/JxUFvunn2Z\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"my absolute all\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I executed it as well as I could.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the end goal, it's about the process.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end goal\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not matter what time it says on the scoreboard, I think in my heart I have already won.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what time\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am so happy that I can race against the best in the world and still come joint-second.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my heart I have won, these are happy tears.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I gave my absolute best every single day and I cannot be upset about that.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am almost an older man here now.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an older man\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not have that relentless pursuit every single day without a sacrifice of some sort - they come in every single form.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that relentless pursuit\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"a sacrifice\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"every single form\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very hard to compete with the younger ones, so I am very happy with that.'\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the younger ones\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty continued to look emotional as he hugged his wife and young child in the stands after coming so close to another Olympic gold.\", \"