m\": 2518, \"to\": 2528}, {\"ngram\": \", Adam.#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/QU5tw5m2fa\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"pieces\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"their emotions\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the best result\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But that was his best result for tonight.'\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his best result\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"tonight\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Double Olympic champion Rebecca Adlington added: 'You could see Adam was genuinely happy.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebecca Adlington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca_Adlington\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adam\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could see they were happy tears.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am just emotional for him because, as an athlete, you know what he has been through.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have achieved nothing compared to Adam - what he has achieved is unbelievable - I can not even get my head around it.\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3093}, {